            <lg xml:id="TK226">
<l>aṟṟā raḻipaci tīrtta laḵtoruvaṉ</l>
<l>peṟṟāṉ poruḷvaip puḻi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The removal of the killing hunger of the poor is the place for one to lay up his wealth.</l>
